Car
Class Car represents a car entity.

The CarDriver class serves as a driver program to test and demonstrate the functionality of the Car class, which represents a car in the automotive domain.
CargoTransport
The CargoTransport interface defines the contract for any class that represents a cargo transport vehicle.
CargoTruck
The CargoTruck class represents a cargo truck, which is a specific type of car with the ability to load and unload cargo.

The Engine class represents the engine component of a car.
